'''南区'''（{{lang-en|South Side}}）是美国[[伊利诺州|伊利诺州]][[庫克縣_(伊利諾伊州)|库克县]][[芝加哥|芝加哥]]市的一个重要组成部分。它的大部分在并入芝加哥市前是独立的镇，如[[海德公園_(芝加哥)|海德公園]]（Hyde Park），是在1889年并入芝加哥市<ref name=A>{{cite web | url = http://www.encyclopedia.chicagohistory.org/pages/53.html | title = Annexation | year = 2005 | work = The Electronic Encyclopedia of Chicago | publisher = Chicago Historical Society | accessdate = September 8, 2008 | last = Cain | first = Louis P. | archive-date = 2008-09-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20080919135149/http://www.encyclopedia.chicagohistory.org/pages/53.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>。 

芝加哥南区最初被定义为[[芝加哥河|芝加哥河]]干流以南的整个城市<ref name="Encarta">{{cite web | url = http://encarta.msn.com/encyclopedia_761576998/Chicago_(city_Illinois).html#s10 | title = Chicago (city, Illinois) | year = 2007 | work = Microsoft Encarta Online Encyclopedia | publisher = Microsoft Corporation | accessdate = August 13, 2007 | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20070813175125/http://encarta.msn.com/encyclopedia_761576998/Chicago_(city_Illinois).html#s10 | archivedate = 2007年8月13日 }}</ref><ref name="CPLFlag">{{cite web | url = http://www.chipublib.org/004chicago/flagtxt.html | title = The Municipal Flag of Chicago | publisher = Chicago Public Library | accessdate = October 28, 2007 | archive-date = 2013-03-30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20130330092054/http://www.chipublib.org/004chicago/flagtxt.html | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但现在不包括[[卢普区|卢普区]]。芝加哥南区拥有多种种族成分，在收入方面也有巨大差距<ref name="EoCSS">{{cite web|url=http://www.encyclopedia.chicagohistory.org/pages/1177.html|title=South Side|accessdate=August 10, 2007|work=The Electronic Encyclopedia of Chicago|year=2005|publisher=Chicago Historical Society|author=Pacyga, Dominic A.|archive-date=2007-10-17|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071017032129/http://www.encyclopedia.chicagohistory.org/pages/1177.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。虽然它拥有贫穷、犯罪率高的名声，<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.huffingtonpost.com/anne-peterson/what-the-south-side-of-ch_b_822511.html#s239377&title=Gas_Explosion_South|title=What the South Side of Chicago Could Learn From Egypt|accessdate=2012-10-04|date=2011-02-14|work=[[The_Huffington_Post|The Huffington Post]]|author=Peterson, Anne|archive-date=2016-09-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160915122956/http://www.huffingtonpost.com/anne-peterson/what-the-south-side-of-ch_b_822511.html#s239377&title=Gas_Explosion_South|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2012/08/19/magazine/obama-poverty.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0|title=What Does Obama Really Believe In?|accessdate=2012-10-04|date=2012-08-15|work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]]|author=Tough, Paul|archive-date=2020-09-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929001337/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/08/19/magazine/obama-poverty.html?pagewanted=all&_r=0|dead-url=no}}</ref> 但现实更加多样化。芝加哥南区的居民从富裕阶层到[[中产阶级|中产阶级]]到[[工人阶级|工人阶级]]再到贫困阶层均有<ref name="SSUCH">{{cite web | url = http://southside.uchicago.edu/History/Housing.html | title = Housing, A Short History | year = 2007 | work = You Are Here | publisher = The University of Chicago | accessdate = August 19, 2007 | archive-date = 2020-11-27 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201127013007/http://southside.uchicago.edu/History/Housing.html | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="UchiMag">{{cite web | url = http://magazine.uchicago.edu/0734/features/stewart.shtml | title = Cinéma vérité | year = 2007 | publisher = The University of Chicago Magazine | accessdate = August 19, 2007 | archive-date = 2020-08-07 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200807125314/http://magazine.uchicago.edu/0734/features/stewart.shtml | dead-url = no }}</ref>。盔甲广场（Armour Square）、Back of the Yards、布里奇波特（Bridgeport）和铂尔曼（Pullman）等社区主要是[[蓝领|蓝领]]居住区，而海德公园（Hyde Park）、杰克逊公园高地区（Jackson Park Highlands District）、建伍（Kenwood）和比佛利（Beverly）则是富裕、[[中产阶级|中产阶级]]和中上阶级居住区<ref name="Incmap">{{cite web| url = http://egov.cityofchicago.org/webportal/COCWebPortal/COC_EDITORIAL/Income_MedianHousehold_1.pdf| format = PDF| title = Chicago Demographics: Median Household Income (as of the 2000 Census)| publisher = CityofChicago.org| accessdate = October 31, 2007}}{{dead link|date=October 2017 |bot=InternetArchiveBot }}</ref>。

南区拥有自己的专业运动队和标志性建筑，博物馆，教育机构，医疗机构和芝加哥的公园系统的主要部分。

[[贝拉克·奥巴马|巴拉克·奧巴馬]][[总统图书馆|總統圖書館]]（Barack Obama Presidential Center）將在該區[[傑克遜公園|傑克遜公園]]內建成。

芝加哥唐人街位于芝加哥南区东北部的盔甲广场区（Armour Square）北部，靠近[[近南区_(芝加哥)|近南区]]。

